  "detailed_description": "Bigger Bikes is a game about riding bikes, in off-road conditions. The gameplay is based on realistic bike control and funny physics. Be careful! You can go into a skid, roll over or fly into a ditch at any time. Overcome difficult mountainous and hilly terrain, ride light or take a load with you, look for the safest route so as not to roll over and lose the delivery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Five vehicles<br></li><li> Realistic bike control<br></li><li> Fascinating mountain landscapes <br></li><li> Hardcore, based on physics</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Bigger Bikes is a game about riding bikes, in off-road conditions. The gameplay is based on realistic bike control and funny physics. Be careful! You can go into a skid, roll over or fly into a ditch at any time. Overcome difficult mountainous and hilly terrain, ride light or take a load with you, look for the safest route so as not to roll over and lose the delivery.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Five vehicles<br></li><li> Realistic bike control<br></li><li> Fascinating mountain landscapes <br></li><li> Hardcore, based on physics</li></ul>",
